File-DirList version 0.04
=========================

File::DirList can be used to get sorted directory content list


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

	DirHandle

